query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `actionModeCache` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `reviewId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `mode` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `content` mediumtext NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `actionModeCache_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `uq_actionModeCache_reviewId_mode` UNIQUE(`reviewId`, `mode`),
  INDEX `idx_actionModeCache_reviewId` (`reviewId`),
  CONSTRAINT `actionModeCache_reviewId_reviews_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`reviewId`) REFERENCES `reviews`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `actionModeCache_userId_users_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`userId`) REFERENCES `users`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
